    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just one glass of wine though... i feel like people do this all the time. i'm not like, heading out to a party or anything, i'm just sitting on my couch. won't the alcohol just help the diazepam reach my system faster so i can actually get some rest? it seems like it would just make the treatment more effective for the night.",
